[We would be grateful for further distribution of the job advertisement=20
below]

In the Theoretical Computer Science group (Chair Computer Science 8) at=20
the Friedrich-Alexander-Universit=C3=A4t Erlangen-N=C3=BCrnberg, we have =
a PhD and=20
a postdoc position available in the DFG-Project "A High Level Language=20
for Programming and Specifying Multi-Effect Algorithms", which is=20
concerned with monad-based semantics and program logics for=20
side-effecting iteration and recursion. The technical part of the=20
project proposal can be made available on request.

The project is supervised by Sergey Goncharov and Lutz Schr=C3=B6der. The=
=20
positions are in the TV-L E13 or E14 pay scale depending on=20
qualification of the applicant; the project duration is three years.

Please enquire or apply by e-mail to

      {lutz.schroeder,sergey.goncharov}@fau.de

Best,

Sergey and Lutz



